  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.1.4">
<l>nāmava ṉivaṉuva ṉavaḷivaḷuvaḷeva</l>
<l>ṭāmavarivaruva ratuvitu vutuvetu</l>
<l>vīmavai yivaiyuvai yavainalan tīṅkavai</l>
<l>yāmavai yāyavai yāyniṉṟa vavarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We, he there, he here, he in between, she there, she here, she in between – which one?</l>
<l>They there, they here, they in between, that, this, that in between – what?</l>
<l>Those that are perishing, these, those ones, those good ones, those bad ones,</l>
<l>those becoming, those who have become – being [all this] it is he who stands there.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
